  "description": "Fix Gallery Card Layout and Display Missing Title\n\nResolve layout issues in gallery card components where excessive bottom padding is present, and ensure gallery titles are properly displayed.\n\nRequirements:\n- Remove or reduce excessive whitespace at the bottom of gallery-card items\n- Display the gallery title on each card (currently hidden or missing)\n- Ensure consistent card height across all gallery items\n- Verify proper spacing between title and other card elements\n- Maintain responsive behavior across different screen sizes\n- Test with various title lengths to prevent overflow or truncation issues\n- Ensure alignment and visual hierarchy within the card remains balanced",
